Hartford Insurance Group , unit New York-based ITT Corp , said higher worldwide premium help boost net income 1986 fourth quarter 88.6 mln dlrs , net income 36.7 mln dlrs 1985 quarter .
For full year , Hartford said earned 329 mln dlrs , 151.4 mln dlrs 1985 .
Hartford said result year aided gain 46.5 mln dlrs sale remaining 52 pct stake Abbey Life Group PLC .
For 1985 , company posted gain 14.3 mln dlrs sale 48 pct Abbey Life .
Hartford said total property-casualty life-health written premium rose 25 pct 1986 , eight billion dlrs , 6.4 billion dlrs 1985 .
